def time_is_semistable(self):
    R = PolynomialRing(QQ, 'x')
    x = R.gen()
    Y = SuperellipticCurve(x^4 - 1, 3)
    v_2 = QQ.valuation(2)
    Y2 = SemistableModel(Y, v_2)
    Y2.is_semistable()
